name: container_1
description: the jar file location of the older version of the project

name: container_2
description: the jar file location of the newer version of the project

name: class_1
description: path of the modified class file in container_1

name: class_2
description: path of the modified class file in container_2

name: compiler_name
description: Java compiler name

name: compiler_major_version
description: Java compiler major version number

name: compiler_minor_version
description: Java compiler minor version number

name: compiler_patch_version
description: Java compiler patch version number

name: compiler_extra_config
description: underlying docker image name used for ecj builds, otherwise '-'

name: project_name
description: name of project. NOTE: This usually corresponds to the jar name, but not always

name: project_major_version_1
description: project major version number for class_1

name: project_major_version_2
description: project major version number for class_2

name: project_minor_version_1
description: project minor version number for class_1, or '-' if absent

name: project_minor_version_2
description: project minor version number for class_2, or '-' if absent

name: project_patch_version_1
description: project patch version number for class_1, or '-' if absent

name: project_patch_version_2
description: project patch version number for class_2, or '-' if absent

name: generated_by_1
description: ID of tool used to generate class_1 source, or '-' if source was present in repo

name: generated_by_2
description: ID of tool used to generate class_2 source, or '-' if source was present in repo

name: bytecode_jep181_1
description: true if pre-JEP181 synthetic outer class accessor methods detected in class_1 bytecode, instead of post-JEP181 'nests'

name: bytecode_jep181_2
description: true if pre-JEP181 synthetic outer class accessor methods detected in class_2 bytecode, instead of post-JEP181 'nests'

name: bytecode_jep280_1
description: true if post-JEP280 invokedynamic string literal concatenation calls detected in class_1 bytecode

name: bytecode_jep280_2
description: true if post-JEP280 invokedynamic string literal concatenation calls detected in class_2 bytecode

name: scope_1
description: Maven scope of class_1 ('main' or 'test')

name: scope_2
description: Maven scope of class_2 ('main' or 'test')

name: n_anon_inner_classes_1
description: number of anonymous inner classes in class_1

name: n_anon_inner_classes_2
description: number of anonymous inner classes in class_2

name: source_compatible
description: true if revapi reports no source-BREAKING changes for methods in this class

name: binary_compatible
description: true if revapi reports no source-BREAKING changes for methods in this class

name: semantic_compatible
description: true if revapi reports no source-BREAKING changes for methods in this class
